@startuml sm_agent_lifecycle
' ============================================================
' Title:     nasim — Agent Lifecycle State Machine
' Boundary:  nasim code agent CLI
' Purpose:   Define agent states and transitions during task execution
' Milestone: v1.0
' Version:   2.0.0
' Source:    docs/audit/audit_2026-06-20_capability-and-architecture.md
' Review:    —
' Note:      Process FSM, not entity lifecycle. SMT ownership rules
'            from sm.md do not apply (documented deviation).
' ============================================================

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<idle>> #E8F5E9
    BackgroundColor<<listening>> #E3F2FD
    BackgroundColor<<thinking>> #FFF3E0
    BackgroundColor<<tool_exec>> #F3E5F5
    BackgroundColor<<responding>> #FCE4EC
    BackgroundColor<<error>> #FFEBEE
    BackgroundColor<<compacting>> #E0F7FA
    BackgroundColor<<awaiting_approval>> #FFF9C4
    BackgroundColor<<planning>> #F1F8E9
}

state "IDLE" as idle <<idle>> : Waiting for user input
state "LISTENING" as listening <<listening>> : Receiving and parsing user input
state "THINKING" as thinking <<thinking>> : LLM processing, generating response or tool calls
state "TOOL_EXEC" as tool_exec <<tool_exec>> : Executing a tool call from LLM
state "RESPONDING" as responding <<responding>> : Streaming final text response to user
state "ERROR" as error <<error>> : Error occurred, displaying error message
state "COMPACTING" as compacting <<compacting>> : Summarizing old exchanges to free context budget
state "AWAITING_APPROVAL" as awaiting_approval <<awaiting_approval>> : PermissionGate waiting for user [y/N]
state "PLANNING" as planning <<planning>> : Plan mode active, tool calls queued not executed

[*] --> idle
idle --> listening : user input received
listening --> thinking : input parsed, messages built
thinking --> responding : LLM returns text (no tool calls)
thinking --> tool_exec : LLM returns tool calls
thinking --> compacting : token_count > budget_threshold
tool_exec --> thinking : tool result appended to messages
tool_exec --> awaiting_approval : safety_mode = ask AND tool.unsafe
awaiting_approval --> tool_exec : user approves [y]
awaiting_approval --> idle : user rejects [N]
compacting --> thinking : compaction complete, messages shortened
responding --> idle : response complete
thinking --> error : LLM call fails
tool_exec --> error : tool execution fails
error --> idle : error displayed

idle --> [*] : /quit or EOF

note right of planning
  Plan mode (Phase 2):
  /plan toggles PLANNING state.
  Tool calls queued, not executed.
  /approve drains queue.
end note

note right of compacting
  ContextCompactor triggered when
  token_count > context_budget.
  Summarizes oldest exchanges via
  secondary LLM call.
end note

note right of awaiting_approval
  PermissionGate in ask mode:
  unsafe tools prompt user [y/N]
  before execution.
end note

@enduml
